input TEMPERATURE
SEND "please enter the temperature" TO DISPLAY
RECIEVE from KEYBOARD
IF TEMPERATURE <18 °C
SEND "Cold the perfect temperature for sleep is 18-20 degrees" TO DISPLAY
IF TEMPERATURE IS >21°C 
SEND "Perfect"
IF TEMPARATURE is <21°C
SEND "No!, the perfect temperature for sleep is 18-21 degrees"
END
